* ''[[The Curse of Chalion]]'' (2001) Hugo, Locus Fantasy, and World Fantasy Awards nominee, 2002<ref name="wwoe2002">{{cite web|url=http://www.worldswithoutend.com/books_year_index.asp?year=2002 |title=2002 Award Winners & Nominees &#124; Science Fiction & Fantasy Books by Award &#124; WWEnd |publisher=Worldswithoutend.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-28}}</ref>
* ''[[Paladin of Souls]]'' (2003) (sequel to ''The Curse of Chalion'') Hugo, Nebula and Locus Fantasy Awards winner, 2004<ref name="wwoe2004">{{cite web|url=http://www.worldswithoutend.com/books_year_index.asp?year=2004 |title=2004 Award Winners & Nominees &#124; Science Fiction & Fantasy Books by Award &#124; WWEnd |publisher=Worldswithoutend.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-28}}</ref>
* ''[[The Hallowed Hunt]]'' (2005) Locus Fantasy Award nominee, 2006<ref name="wwoe2006">{{cite web|url=http://www.worldswithoutend.com/books_year_index.asp?year=2006 |title=2006 Award Winners & Nominees &#124; Science Fiction & Fantasy Books by Award &#124; WWEnd |publisher=Worldswithoutend.com |date= |accessdate=2014-01-28}}</ref>

