Blackstone Audio produces CD editions, MP3, [[Playaway]], and [[compact cassette|cassette]] versions of  ''The Curse of Chalion'', ''Paladin of Souls'', ''The Hallowed Hunt'', ''The Sharing Knife Vol 1: Beguilement'', ''The Sharing Knife Vol 2: Legacy'', ''The Sharing Knife Vol 3: Passage'' and ''The Sharing Knife Vol 4: Horizon''.  All of these titles are also available from [[Audible.com]] and [[emusic]].com.

